Overview

[Est 9:1](../../../bib/kjv/est009.htm#001.md), The Jews slay their enemies,
with the ten sons of Haman; [Est 9:12](../../../bib/kjv/est009.htm#012.md),
Ahasuerus, at the request of Esther, grants another day of slaughter,
and Haman's sons to be hanged; [Est
9:20](../../../bib/kjv/est009.htm#020.md), The two days of Purim are made
festival.

